{"tid":240822,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"話比人知溫書溫通宵係咩心態","createTime":"2017-05-12T16:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T13:32:29.000Z","uid":23720,"like":24,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cceda68a74008edb661c6cfccbbfe5080909da3b","tid":240822,"uid":23720,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"早排考試成日都有人話自己溫到幾點幾點<br />\n甚至溫通宵<br />\n呢個話零晨1點<br />\n嗰個話3點<br />\n有個就話通宵咁<br />\n其實有必要鬥咩<br />\n<br />\n溫到咁夜都考得差嘅<br />\n應該話你臨急抱佛腳<br />\n定係話你資質差<br />\n<br />\n想話比人知你考試有努力溫書<br />\n考得差只係份卷難？定係想賴落個prof教得廢？<br />\n有冇諗過係自己讀書嘅方法有問題<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明同人講溫到咁夜係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5640847b2add7e3805d745d4d5aba91ebe389bef","tid":240822,"uid":116181,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"有料到就唔洗溫咁耐啦<br />\n<br />\n通頂你估真係對住本書咩<br />\n<br />\nching ho ball"},{"pid":"2e9ced504a6ea69a95fb70c6834b315e29ba857d","tid":240822,"uid":23720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有料到就唔洗溫咁耐啦<br />\n<br />\n通頂你估真係對住本書咩<br />\n<br />\nching ho ball</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溫咁耐都炒嘅<br />\n係咪應該話領悟力低(姐係蠢)"},{"pid":"de231647336811998d3d029483cc8d541a6de22b","tid":240822,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有料到就唔洗溫咁耐啦<br />\n<br />\n通頂你估真係對住本書咩<br />\n<br />\nching ho ball</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溫咁耐都炒嘅<br />\n係咪應該話領悟力低(姐係蠢)</blockquote><br />\n唔比人前一日先溫"},{"pid":"75863c8c082f910ce9ecb0b8af65bd045a9a630b","tid":240822,"uid":80503,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"抒發下溫幾耐書都得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989ed5cf3bc039119e4f881c79ec0985359bff81","tid":240822,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:34:13.000Z","msg":"可能人哋想講最後一日先溫都a<img sr